Kayaking Tracker

A beginner Python project designed to track kayaking sessions and basic performance data.

Features
Records:
Distance paddled
Moving time
Session feeling score
Calculates average pace in minutes per mile
Gives simple feedback based on session difficulty
Beginning work on storing multiple sessions using lists
Why I Built This

I paddle regularly and wanted to build a project around something real rather than a generic coding exercise. The long-term goal is to expand this into a more advanced performance tracker with:

Session history
Progress tracking
Speed analysis
Resistance tracking
K1 vs K2 comparisons
Potential Garmin data integration later on
What I'm Learning

This project is helping me practise:

Python basics
Variables and calculations
Conditionals
Lists and data storage
Structuring larger projects
Status

Work in progress 🚧
